  "body": "Current Flow:\r\n\r\nOne clicks on a .md file, it loads file with docgen viewer with an EDIT button. If user wants to make changes on the file, can click on EDIT button and new tab in editor opened with raw content.\r\n\r\nSuggested Flow:\r\n\r\nOne clicks on .md file, file with raw content opens. User can make changes to the file if required and can click on green play button in editor to have the preview. Preview will be loaded with EDIT button.",
